reviewText: Walt Disney World Resort is a 57 minute video that will give you a pretty good preview of the 4 theme parks within Disney World. The video will not cover all the theme parks rides within Disney World but it a very good start. I would recommend this video as research before going to Disney World. Going to Disney World can be an overwhelming experience and any pre-planning can definitely help.Thank you for reading my review.
summary: Ultimate Walt Disney World is a good video to watch before you go to Disney World

reviewText: If you're into the thrill rides, you'll love this. I'm not into roller coasters or things that move too quickly or unexpectedly, but this did make me aware of some rides that I didn't know existed. I've been to Walt Disney World, but obviously I didn't see everything. I will probably watch this again. If you're planning a trip to Disney World, watch this!
